  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the present study is to evaluate the effect of sleep duration on weight loss
      of obese and overweight adult when they are in a weight loss plan (NovinDiet Protocol). The
      investigators aim is to compare the effects of short term sleep duration with normal sleep
      duration with respect to body weight (and abdominal adiposity).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
